long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Nozee is an app that allows you to prove ownership over an email domain in a completely private way by verifying a personal JWT with zero knowledge proofs. This is an extension to extract your JWT after logging into Open AI.

Learn more about Nozee: https://prove.email/blog/jwt
